high_descs: Turn to face the sink on the right.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave for a few seconds.
Bring the mug to the wooden rack.
Place the mug on the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug on the wooden rack.

high_descs: Go to the sink to your right.
Remove the cup on the right from the sink.
Take the cup to the microwave.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
That the cup to the shelves behind you and to your right.
Place the cup on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the white cup from the sink.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup in it, heat it up, and take the cup out of it.
Turn left, walk past the fridge, then turn left towards the wooden shelf on your right.
Place the cup next to the salt shaker on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed cup on the wooden shelf.
